The '''A486''' is an A road in [[Wales]] linking [[New Quay]], [[Ceredigion]], with the [[A484 road|A484]] in Saron (Llangeler), Carmarthenshire.

==Route==
The road begins in New Quay near the waterfront area and (north to south) passes through or by the settlements of:
*[[Maenygroes]]
*[[Cross Inn]]
*Synod Inn (junction with [[A487 road|A487]] and B4338)
*[[Capel Cynon]]
*[[Ffostrasol]]
*[[Croes-Lan]]
*[[Horeb, Carmarthenshire|Horeb]] (junction with [[A475 road|A475]])
*[[Llandysul]] (bypassed, junction with B4624)
*[[Dolgran]]
*[[Pentrecwrt]]
The A486 finishes at the junction with the A484 in Saron.  

